To get into the spirit of the enterprise, I'm going to pick 4 rules for images and 4 rules for sounds now, then spend no more than 5 minutes creating each and any necessary remaining time documenting the process and results. I.e., up to 40 minutes of making plus x minutes of documentation. This time frame should test the efficacy of the rules (which were requested to take no longer than 5-10 minutes to implement), allow me to try multiple processes in a short time frame, and focus the attention while seeing what interesting things can result. I will choose with some randomness plus critical analysis (these will be the first rule sets I see that I feel capable of executing currently and which sound like they'd making something interesting). I will provide pictures and audio recordings and will also note commentary on each rule after the listing (and after I have "used" the rule).\
\
Here are the 4 image rule sets:\
