\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 \cb2 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}9) You should now have a contraption that is symmetrical if you fold it on its vertical axis. Now fold it on its vertical axis, making sure the mini-triangle is left exposed.\cb1 \
